# SIT305 Task 2.1P - Travel Companion Converter

## Project Description

This project is an Android application developed using Java in Android Studio.  
The app provides simple conversion functions including currency, temperature, and fuel conversions.

---

## Features

- Currency conversion (e.g. USD to AUD)
- Temperature conversion (Celsius, Fahrenheit, Kelvin)
- Fuel conversion
- Simple and user-friendly interface

---

## Technologies Used

- Java
- Android Studio
- XML (for UI design)
- ConstraintLayout

---

## How to Run

1. Open the project in Android Studio  
2. Sync Gradle and build the project  
3. Run the app on an emulator or physical device  

---

## Project Structure

- `MainActivity.java` → Handles the main logic and conversion functions  
- `activity_main.xml` → Defines the user interface  
- `strings.xml` → Stores text resources  

